{"tid":447594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［Flirt界大絕］攝影師道歉：剛看你的照片，忍不任DIY了","createTime":"2017-10-25T12:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T12:19:38.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b43ce965d8c71e97521bcff74e0beef178c40dd1","tid":447594,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:19:38.000Z","msg":"真的是「色」影師！外拍模特兒Una日前在臉書爆料，表示從2016年間遇到一位吳姓攝影師邀約外拍，不僅傳別人的露點照給她參考。後來兩人外拍結束後，突然又接到對方的道歉訊息，自白看著她的照片偷偷「打手槍」，變態行為讓她當場罵出髒話，並且將對話在網路上公開，要大家小心該名攝影師。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20171025004974-260803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20171025004974-260803&d=ptukkp76HDA20JbiMFt6Ocn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=58eb6970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20171025004974-260803</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/201858_8933bddb5dc7c51b28bb4c667c3075ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F201858_8933bddb5dc7c51b28bb4c667c3075ed.jpg&h=36c2e946&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/201900_2f2cd5133d6d31ef2b113c3557e420dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F201900_2f2cd5133d6d31ef2b113c3557e420dd.jpg&h=1a0645c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/201905_6ebd71a796f48aa53905dc4af277cba0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F201905_6ebd71a796f48aa53905dc4af277cba0.jpg&h=ec890dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢招好work,唔信試下"}]}